Tools "OOovirg" for Open Office has not an installer. It's a "zip file". Then, 
we create a directory "OOovirg", and we unzip "OOovirg.zip" inside.

File name: OOovirg.zip
Directory name: OOovirg
Version: 1.0.0.1
Installed-Size: 231 Ko
Description: OOOVirg will enable you to transform the point of the numeric 
keypad into comma, which will enable you to seize more easily and quickly the 
data with OpenOffice.

Source: http://www.via.ecp.fr/~remi/win/ooovirg/ooovirg.php3